text: Full details of the statistical analysis are in the supplementary appendix. Briefly, primary and secondary endpoints were compared between the study arms using Fisher's exact test. Prespecified analyses were conducted using intention to treat (ITT). Reactions per dose were compared between study arms using Generalized Estimated Equations with logit link. Pvalues ≤0.05 were considered significant.
